    "Descarga la cartola desde tu banco (CSV, OFX o QFX) y súbela aquí. Reviso cuáles ya tienes y marco los repetidos para que no entren dos veces.": "Download the statement from your bank (CSV, OFX or QFX) and upload it here. I check which ones you already have and flag the duplicates so they don't get added twice.",
